name: Marshal Hydraulics
overview:
Established in the year 2002, we, “Marshal Hydraulics”, are engaged in manufacturing, supplying and exporting an extensive range of Material Handling Equipment to our customers. Our products are appreciated widely by the customers owing to their features like Durability, Reliability, High performance, Functional Efficiency, Perfect finish and Easy installation.

Product Profile: We are counted amongst the renowned manufacturer & exporter of wide range of Material Handling Equipment which includes Hydraulic Beam Hand Pallet Truck, Hydraulic Hand Lift Mobile Floor Jib Crane, Hydraulic Lift Table, Hydraulic Drum Lifter/Tilter, Semi Electric Stacker, Two Cylinder Lift, etc.

Our Team: Engineers and technicians Quality controllers Researchers Skilled labourers Sales and marketing personnel

Manufacturing Unit: We have a state-of-the-art infrastructure spread across a wide area. The entire infrastructure is divided properly into a number of units that cater to the various processes going on in the organization. Manufacturing, packaging, quality control are the units to name a few. Moreover, we also have the latest technology and advanced machinery employed for the purpose of manufacturing in order to serve our clients with the world-class products.

Our Quality Assurance: Being a client-centric organization, we are engaged in offering quality-assured products to our customers. These products are manufactured using high-grade quality of raw material. The products offered by us are widely appreciated for their supreme quality, perfect finish, resistance against corrosion, robust construction and easy installation.

Industries We Cater To: We are counted among the leading organizations engaged in offering a wide and excellent range of Machine Handling Equipment to our esteemed patrons. These machines have been furnished in compliance with international quality standards using the best quality raw material procured from some of the renowned vendors of the market.
